{"tid":2397914,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–癌症所導致的體重流失","createTime":"2021-02-06T22:15:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T10:33:40.000Z","uid":38861,"like":60,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2ac8cc06e8e129f6fdc64884096c92beff65a024","tid":2397914,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T22:15:28.000Z","msg":"不少的癌症病人均會出現體重及BMI急速下降的情況，肌肉會出現萎縮，脂肪組織亦有機會有所消耗，這現象稱之為Cancer-associated cachexia(CAC)。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9zbeY0X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9zbeY0X.jpg&h=d88c5840&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n與厭食症不同的是，體重的流失並沒能依靠增加進食來進行完全填補。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）CAC的形成，是腫瘤與身體多種器官互動後所得出的結果，箇中涉及新陳代謝及荷爾蒙的轉變。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqhUY00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmqhUY00.jpg&h=c0b1bb16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）從圖中所見，老鼠出現腫瘤約21日後，腿部肌肉出現萎縮，與人類的CAC現象吻合。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6j7JSk2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6j7JSk2.png&h=5030e76e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPTHrP是一種某類型的腫瘤釋放到血管的蛋白質，而往老鼠注射PTHrP蛋白質抗體的話，肌肉的萎縮程度亦有所緩和。<br />\n<br />\n只可是，往健康老鼠注射PTHrP蛋白質的話，肌肉並不會貿然萎縮，而往出現腫瘤的老鼠注射PTHrP蛋白質的話，肌肉萎縮的程度反會更加劇烈。<br />\n<br />\n這亦證明，PTHrP蛋白質只是導致癌症時候肌肉萎縮的其中一道組件，還需要癌細胞另外的付出才可達成。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n癌症所帶來的CAC現象，會導致藥物對其他正常器官出現更強烈的副作用及毒性。這變相需要降低用藥的劑量作出配合，因而減低了滅癌的效率。<br />\n<br />\n因此，現今科學家亦在努力嘗試找出CAC的整套機制，務求找出有效的醫學方法制止CAC的產生。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMIWHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=d7be4b93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMIWHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=93ba0aea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基於WhatsApp/Facebook等問題，IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/nature13528\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fnature13528&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMIWHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=87691224\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/nature13528</a>"},{"pid":"45e661219c940f42b5e4a9dbe7483c19ef82079d","tid":2397914,"uid":199689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T22:17:02.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"9f3d9ae2eba05d3ecbe1bcf7d5c6353e92c93fb1","tid":2397914,"uid":10133,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T22:23:34.000Z","msg":"日日食大芋，希望比飯多纖維健康啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf75b7ddb741a76f7039d87a75eb70f560695bc3","tid":2397914,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T22:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9329ac5fe3df95a21057f0d387d53921057ae5e","tid":2397914,"uid":38861,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9f3d9ae2eba05d